{
  "stem": "3524.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How many-- or what percentage would you say were the Jewish prisoners in--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never was pertinent to that information.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could tell by looking at their characteristics that many of them may have been Jewish, but it was difficult to tell whether they were Jewish or Bulgarian.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not that much of a racial [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] expert on facial characteristics.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't ask, and they didn't tell us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of them we knew were Jewish or had been in concentration camps because we could see the tattoos of the numbers on their arms or something of that nature.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the other-- the senior pharmacist and myself would concentrate just on filling the needs of the wards.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The wards would have some basic needs like cough syrups and antacids and [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] the blood they got from another source.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't handle the blood, but they would come down and get some of the basic pain relievers and expectorants and things of that nature.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then if there were some specific needs, then we'd see if our stock would fulfill that, and we'd send that medication on up to the wards.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I never came in contact with the patients themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The nurses did most of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We never talked a whole lot about it at the time, except to make general comments about how generally poor their condition had been and how encouraged they were when they saw progress.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, we never did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You reflect upon it, but I think you take it in, in its context and store it away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think a lot of it we push behind us.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
